    <skos:changeNote>Change in v0.2:
- rdfs:domain moved from noria:Employee to foaf:Agent.
- name and label moved from teamManagesResource to agentManagesResource.
- Removing rdfs:range noria:Resource for noria:Resource and noria:NetworkLink compatibility.</skos:changeNote>
    <rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/noria/ontology/"/>
  </rdf:Description>
